oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Biff Collie radio services advertisements
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Recorded of various advertisements for Biff Collie's radio services, including Inside Nashville, live morning news reports, and country music trivia.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Biff Collie talks about creating a live morning news report, including traffic updates -- Collie aircheck example on Dolly Parton -- Collie aircheck example on Hank Williams Jr. and Willie Nelson -- Collie aircheck example on various country artist trivia -- Collie talks further about his morning drive report services (incomplete) -- Collie talks further about his radio services (incomplete)
